snippet: Younis Makhyoun, a 58-year-old cleric and trained dentist, was selected in a consensus vote to lead the Salafi Al-Nour party.
abstract: Younis Makhyoun is elected leader of Salafi Al Nour party, Egypt's largest ultraconservative Islamist party.
